Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.55,0:01:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the protocol,\NKosta?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.32,0:01:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Raymond?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.02,0:01:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.79,0:01:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The last time I saw you,\Nyou said you were going to\Nmeet your fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.82,0:01:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You may very well\Nbe about to meet yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.86,0:01:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.33,0:01:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.73,0:01:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.16,0:01:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.80,0:01:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hear\Nfrom your lips
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,how the plan\Nwas supposed to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.44,0:01:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,To begin with?\NYou were supposed to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.48,0:01:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Elizabeth would be given\Nspecific instructions
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.21,0:01:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,on how to\Nmake her way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I would be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.58,0:01:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Elizabeth is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.39,0:02:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,For several years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.92,0:02:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't think something was\Nwrong when she\Nnever showed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.72,0:02:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you never told me\Nhow long to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.83,0:02:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So I kept\Nthe lanterns burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.76,0:02:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The noble lighthouse keeper\Nat the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be poetic, if you\Nhadn't betrayed my trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I would never.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.21,0:02:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The recordings\Nfor Elizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.11,0:02:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw me put them\Ninside the safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.04,0:02:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. In the screening room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No one has\Nbeen in there since.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why did I find these\Non the other side\Nof the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.39,0:02:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Bocce balls.\NI figure when in Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in Montenegro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sciatica's acting up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't been\Nin this much pain\Nsince I threw out my back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,dancing at a sock hop in 1974.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that?\NThat's your fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He and his bocce balls\Nare here
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.91,0:02:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,to find out\Nwhat really happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.08,0:02:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you slept well, Kosta.\NIt's going to be a long day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Director, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.43,0:03:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Agent Mojtabai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm-- I'm Mr. Mojta--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.47,0:03:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Aram.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.67,0:03:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How did I forget\Nhow to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I was shocked to see\Nyour name on my phone sheet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.28,0:03:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How've you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.34,0:03:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I've been better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot.\NYou actually do honesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the last couple months\Nhaven't been the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Things didn't quite work out\Nat the Bureau.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.55,0:03:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.39,0:03:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The task force I was on\Ngot shut down
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.29,0:03:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the death\Nof a colleague, and, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.86,0:03:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't find\Nmy passion in it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.43,0:03:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant I'm sorry\Nto hear you say it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You may not remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but commiseration's\Nnot my strong suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.77,0:03:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean,\Nif we're being honest.\NOh, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, Nick, uh, that--\Nthat's why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Because what I remember\Nis that you are\Ncompletely selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This is\Na million-dollar idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.39,0:04:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'm interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you know how most security\Nsystems are defensive, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They detect a threat\Nand shut it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this software--\Nthis software is offensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.54,0:04:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,When it detects an intrusion,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.14,0:04:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,it activates its own\Nbuilt-in Trojan rootkit\Nto attack the intruder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.74,0:04:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It then throws out\Ncolossal floods
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,of junk traffic\Nto clog them up
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.98,0:04:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,while it eviscerates\Ntheir operating system\Nin the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.18,0:04:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That is not\Na million-dollar idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a billion-dollar one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.49,0:04:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This won't just\Nprotect people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It will actively\Ndiscourage black hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll revolutionize\Ntech security.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?\NThat is what I was going for,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but I have no idea how to\Nturn my idea into a business,\Nwhich is why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, um, if, uh--\Nif you're too busy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.27,0:05:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,or, you know, need, um,\Nsome time to think it over--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.31,0:05:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I am too busy,\Nand I've already\Nthought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.88,0:05:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You've reached\NNaamah Mojtabai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.15,0:05:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave a message\Nand have a blessed day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Uh, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I could--\NI could really use, um--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.16,0:05:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I could use a Mom Talk\Nright about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well, I have\Nmy first, uh, briefing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,with the Director of National\NIntelligence this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and I am low-key freaking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, if you get this, like,\Nin the next 10 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can call me back\Nor so, that would be super,\Num, super.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.01,0:05:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.41,0:05:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo! Whoa! Whoa, whoa, whoa!\NWhoa, whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.98,0:05:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Greetings\Nfrom El Conejo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.98,0:05:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd thought\Nof everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.65,0:05:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A villa that no one knew\NI owned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:05:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A place of peace\Nand quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.39,0:06:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A place where Elizabeth could\Nlisten and prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,0:06:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She was\Nto retrieve the box,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.90,0:06:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,sit right here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And learn the business.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.24,0:06:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,From you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I put all of it\Ninto these recordings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Every bit of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I wouldn't be there\Nto help her,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.95,0:06:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but I thought perhaps\Nmy words could,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that they would provide\Nwhatever might be needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And Kosta's job\Nwas to wait for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And to bring her here\Nwhen she arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So she could\Nopen the safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.53,0:06:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The safe\Nis one-of-a-kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I had it constructed\Nin Switzerland
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to my specifications.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Two thumbprints in the world\Ncould open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.08,0:06:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine and/or Elizabeth's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And you put this box\Ninside of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.12,0:07:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And a few days ago,\NI found it\Nin a dead cop's vault
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,5,000 miles\Naway from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The safe looks untouched.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you think\Nthey got inside it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.56,0:07:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hence the bocce balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been over it\Nand over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.77,0:07:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So we just go over it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.97,0:07:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And expect\Na different result?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You do know that's\Nthe definition of insanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.38,0:07:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Panabaker gave you a month\Nto identify who killed\NDoug Koster
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,before all those charges\Nagainst you are reimposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it would be\Ninsane of us
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.85,0:07:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,not to do everything\Nthat we can
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to prevent that\Nfrom happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.85,0:07:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm living\Nin purgatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Worse, it feels like\NCharlene and Agnes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.76,0:07:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,are living there with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey,\Nanyone seen Aram today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not in yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.70,0:07:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't seen him, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you can\Ndrop the "sir."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.93,0:07:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest,\NI never liked it much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.60,0:07:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I prefer "Harold."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Harold, it's not\Nlike Aram to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.04,0:07:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but he had\Nhis first meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:07:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,with National Intelligence\Ntoday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:07:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he had to run home after\Nand change his shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.78,0:08:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. Or his shorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I know we're on the clock\Nwith the investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,but if he needs a pep talk\Nabout what his new\Nresponsibilities are,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm the one\Nwho should give it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.87,0:08:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Mojtabai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\NHe called me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.97,0:08:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he wanted\Nto have a mom talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You said he called.\NWhat else did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.95,0:08:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.48,0:08:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He left a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.38,0:08:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Please find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.11,0:09:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My package has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought there'd be\Nmore to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.52,0:09:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.66,0:09:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Don Francisco\NLuis Marquez.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.86,0:09:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,El Conejo to my best friends\Nand worst enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.40,0:09:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I know who you are,\NSpecial Agent Mojtabai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And you stole from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get this, like,\Nin the next 10 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can call me back\Nor so, that would be super,\Num, super.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo! Whoa! Whoa, whoa, whoa!\NWhoa, whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.99,0:09:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Greetings from El Conejo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.56,0:09:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That came\Nfrom Aram's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.73,0:09:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The entire abduction\Nwas recorded.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.90,0:10:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's El Conejo,\Nand what's he want with Aram?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.17,0:10:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,As to the what,\NI haven't the foggiest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The who\NI can help you with.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.67,0:10:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Dembe and I once chased\N"The Rabbit"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.14,0:10:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,along an underground river\Nin the jungle in Quintana Roo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,El Conejo\Nis Don Marquez?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.98,0:10:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Marquez Cartel.\NThe cocaine traffickers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Cocaine\Nwas their business.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.09,0:10:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now they traffic\Nin a different cash crop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what it takes\Nto grow one of these?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I never used\Nto interest myself\Nin such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.19,0:10:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm more\Nof an import/export man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Avocados are\Na multibillion-dollar industry
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,run by family farming\Noperations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Or it was,\Nbefore the cartels took over
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,through kidnapping,\Ntorture, and murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about that the next time\Nyou order a Cobb salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.61,0:10:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I gotta say, I-I'm still,\Nuh, wondering why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.85,0:10:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You know why,\Nyou magician, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You made an entire\Ntractor trailer of my product
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.39,0:11:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,disappear into thin air\Non its way over the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.40,0:11:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm out half a million,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and my competitors\Nthink I'm soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, I have no idea\Nwhere your truck is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If I did,\NI would tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.34,0:11:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, this is--\NUh, this is terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.01,0:11:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I put in military-grade\Nfirewalls,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.74,0:11:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,elliptic curve cryptography--\Nall of it state-of-the-art
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to protect my supply chains\Nand travel lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.48,0:11:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's terrifying\Nis that a piece of malware\Nchewed through it like a--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.36,0:11:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a termite\Nthrough balsa wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.43,0:11:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Marquez runs\Nhis whole cartel
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,through a notoriously\Nsophisticated server system.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's a connection\Nto Aram,\Nyou have to assume that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not much of a lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The Scripps Brothers.\NThey built the server.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.01,0:11:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Marquez\Nwanted my guy to do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.68,0:11:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but my guy's exclusive to me\Nand has a curfew--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And a very stern mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So he recommended\Nthe Scripps Brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:12:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd pay them a visit myself,\Nbut I'm unavailable\Nat the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll get you an address\Nfor the Scripps.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.02,0:12:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the best place\Nto start.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got the wrong guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I-I've worked on\Na lot of programs,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've never designed\Nanything in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,to hurt someone\Nor-- or cause--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.67,0:12:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Armando.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.21,0:12:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It took my team\Nhalf the day to find it\Nburied in the malware.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.71,0:12:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you acted alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.12,0:12:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you did it\Nfor the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't particularly care.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.42,0:12:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But this has your name\Nall over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.66,0:12:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If I didn't have to kill you,\NI'd hire you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.30,0:12:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa!\NStop, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.73,0:12:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, please.\NStop, stop, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you do whatever\Nyou're planning to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,can I please-- can I please\Ntake a look at that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.51,0:12:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to hand you\Nmy computer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,After everything\Nyou've done?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.51,0:12:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, I have no idea\Nwhere your shipment is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not know\Nwhat that program is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.65,0:13:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you give me\Nthat laptop, maybe--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.35,0:13:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I can\Nhelp you figure this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.32,0:13:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Teddy, who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.69,0:13:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know,\N'cause he doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.19,0:13:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I mention\Nmy sciatica?\NTeddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.70,0:13:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Like getting poked in\Nthe tenderloin by a narwhal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.94,0:13:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to go in?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.10,0:13:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If Teddy says\NKosta doesn't know\Nwho broke into the safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.27,0:13:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,he doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to find the answer\Nsome other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.11,0:13:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you\Nknow the answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.05,0:13:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Not you. You.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.79,0:13:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of you\Nhave been arrested
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.19,0:13:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,by the NSA\Nseven times each?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.79,0:13:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Eight for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.73,0:13:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And, Ritchie, you can't even\Ntouch a computer in Norway
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,without the threat\Nof immediate arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.47,0:13:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you piss off Norway\Nthat bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.57,0:13:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Lawyer. Lawyer. Lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.81,0:14:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, geek squad, we don't\Ncare about how many gigabytes
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you move around\Nin your mother's basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,An FBI agent is missing\Nand the clock's ticking\Non his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Suit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're not gonna like\Nwhat comes next.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.09,0:14:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's all our stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And seeing\Nhow it was used
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.43,0:14:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to help build\Na drug cartel's firewall,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.73,0:14:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the FBI will be\Nimpounding all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.94,0:14:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We just did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.54,0:14:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, though.\NYou'll get it all back.\NEventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a $5,000\N8K monitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.15,0:14:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We're real clumsy\Naround here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.51,0:14:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me get you a receipt\Nfor that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.18,0:14:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We can do this all day long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.62,0:14:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you wanna\Nhelp us out, fellas,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.29,0:14:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and maybe we'll give you\Nthis cart of crap back\Nin one piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of it, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.\NJust don't bust anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad code is--\Nis like a bad recipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:15:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A pinch of this,\Na dash of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,To reverse engineer it,\Nthough, you--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.34,0:15:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're working\Nwithout a cookbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.37,0:15:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in the States?\NNo one told me\Nyou were coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.07,0:15:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a good time, Antonio.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.28,0:15:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll talk about it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.45,0:15:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear it\Nfrom my brother--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here on business.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Samuel works\Nin the business.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You go to college.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There. We talked.\NNow go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.42,0:15:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.83,0:15:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens here, I don't\Nwant you to be a part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What about\Nwhat I want?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I see you, what?\NTwice a year?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.\NSic the goons on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop me a postcard\Nnext time you're around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Or don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.41,0:15:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Mr. Marquez,\NI found something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.85,0:15:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, uh, this here,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,this building block\Nis part of a longer code
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I wrote for a program\Ncalled Greylock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.02,0:15:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why I signed my name\Nto it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.95,0:15:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,As a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.19,0:15:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So this was all you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:16:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No. No, this--\Nthe rest of this isn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.93,0:16:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody stole my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.33,0:16:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is\Nthe Marquez network.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.44,0:16:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You get in and out\Njust like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.04,0:16:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We built a back door.\NSue us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do you\Nwant to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.94,0:16:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything that tells us\Nwhere Marquez took our agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.45,0:16:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't even have to look\Nthat hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy you're missing's\Nsome kind of tech wizard,\Nyeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a user\Nin the network now\Npoking around at everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.62,0:16:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's some serious\Nbandwidth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you get us\Na location?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.19,0:16:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I wrote some of this,\Nbut someone weaponized\Nthe rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The rootkit I wrote\Nto attack intruders
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,was used to gut\Nyour firewall
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and gain access\Nto your shipping lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There is somebody out there\Nwho targeted you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and they used\Nmy work to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.97,0:16:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.07,0:16:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone built\Nan apex predator.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You could use it\Nto rob banks,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.71,0:16:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to disrupt utility services,\Ntake down power grids.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:16:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I just want\Nthe shipment back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this? How the hell\Ndid you get this number?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I have your missing product.\NHalf a million. Cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.99,0:17:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call in one hour\Nwith delivery instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.87,0:17:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Get Samuel.\NAnd lock up the agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.70,0:17:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll deal with him later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.11,0:17:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Elizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you're comfortable,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.94,0:17:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,sitting down\Nwith something good to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.18,0:17:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's always plenty to eat\Nin the larder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.82,0:17:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So please feel free\Nat any time
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to shut me up\Nand help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.52,0:17:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're watching this,\NI must be dead
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.36,0:17:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and the business\Nmust be yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.90,0:17:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.53,0:17:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And excited for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And worried,\Nas you might expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.18,0:17:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with all the gunfire\Nand killers in my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.75,0:18:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never really worried\Nabout myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been much too busy\Nworrying about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.99,0:18:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God, what a pain\Nin the ass I've been.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.79,0:18:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What lies ahead is a glorious,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.43,0:18:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,treacherous, and, I hope,\Nrewarding journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.07,0:18:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'll permit me,\NI'd like to share with you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.71,0:18:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,some things that I've learned\Nover a lifetime of bad deeds
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.01,0:18:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and good intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.85,0:18:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's take a walk\Ntogether one last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations,\Nyou genius son-of-a--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.00,0:18:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it.\NYou know what this means?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.04,0:18:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It means we can start planning\Nto sell this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:19:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I, uh-- I still think\Nwe should tinker.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some diagnostics I\Nwant to take another look at--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Aram, you're killing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.81,0:19:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not ready\Ntill it's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,When?\NThe next epoch?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.58,0:19:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We have\Nthe VitasNow report.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.42,0:19:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They gave us\Na clean bill of health.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.28,0:19:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We paid a third party\Nfor their assessment--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.69,0:19:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,To find flaws, problems,\Ndata gaps,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,things we could've missed,\Nright?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They're only one company.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.93,0:19:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Who double-checked\Neverything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Our I's are dotted,\NT's are crossed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.73,0:19:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I read it. You read it.\NRelax. It's time to celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but they did, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.23,0:19:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,point out a few glitches\Nwith peripherals--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please, no jargon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I don't\Nspeak circuit board.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't spot anything that\Ncouldn't be patched up easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.68,0:19:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Bottom line--\Nthey were happy for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm happy for us,\N'cause we're gonna be\Nstinking rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.65,0:19:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You know\Nwhat we need now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,More champagne\Nand a strip club.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I-I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.32,0:19:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I, uh-- I actually\Nhave dinner plans
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,with my parents tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Aram, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're killing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,FBI!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.04,0:20:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,FBI! Hands! Hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.78,0:20:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, bud.\NHow's your morning going?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.95,0:20:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd you find me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.08,0:20:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,HRT is clearing the space.\NNo sign of Marquez.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, he got a ransom call\Nabout avocados.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently guacamole\Nis the new angel dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.19,0:20:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We managed\Nto bag this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.43,0:20:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hope\Nhe knows something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.16,0:20:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot to the shipping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.20,0:20:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But the most crucial part\Nof shipping--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.24,0:20:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sun Tzu wrote,\N"The greatest victory
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.87,0:20:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,is that which requires\Nno battle."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.54,0:20:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I would agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to make your enemy\Nyour friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,create a problem for them\Nand then solve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.65,0:20:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll want to take notes now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The following is a list\Nof 12 wines
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,that pair with everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.42,0:20:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I've said a lot\Nabout the mechanics
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:20:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,of how to operate my--\Nuh, your empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But much more important\Nthan that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,is managing\Nthe emotional reality
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.60,0:21:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,of running this enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.17,0:21:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And to do that, you must\Nunderstand one concept\Nabove all else.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You have thousands\Nof talented people
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.55,0:21:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,who work for and with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,thousands of people\Nwho you are responsible for.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.02,0:21:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But at the end of the day,\Nyou're alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.87,0:21:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nick. Uh, me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.97,0:21:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to talk.\NUh, you have my number.\NUh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.70,0:21:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go to a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.04,0:21:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I got a better idea--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.77,0:21:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Us figuring out\Nwhy you were kidnapped
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.41,0:21:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,by a bloodthirsty\Navocado cartel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.41,0:21:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, the why is easy--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Marquez thinks I hacked\Ninto his system,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.61,0:21:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,accessed\Nhis delivery routes,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.22,0:21:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and stole his product,\Nbut it wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.29,0:22:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But he found your digital\Nsignature in his system.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.05,0:22:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Uh, which means\Nmy Greylock source code
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.69,0:22:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,was stolen\Nby our avocado thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.83,0:22:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Who had access to it,\Nbesides you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.73,0:22:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, my former\Nbusiness partner, Nick,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.46,0:22:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but he doesn't know HTML\Nfrom hieroglyphics,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.67,0:22:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and, for like a second,\Nthis third-party\Nrisk assessment firm
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.90,0:22:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,we hired to spotlight\Nany glitches.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.77,0:22:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It was early on,\Nbut they definitely had a copy\Nof unlocked source code.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.21,0:22:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I make a suggestion?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.61,0:22:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.28,0:22:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we have\Ntwo avenues here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.28,0:22:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone set up Aram.\NWe need to know who.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.68,0:22:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We also need\Nto track Marquez.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.65,0:22:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A man like that is never\Nin the States long.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.22,0:22:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This may be our one shot\Nat getting a cartel leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.62,0:22:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So we divide and conquer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.26,0:22:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Aram follows up with\Nthe third-party company.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.99,0:22:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's in charge there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.53,0:22:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring them in,\Nget to the bottom of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.07,0:22:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest of you should focus
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.90,0:22:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,on getting whatever\Ninformation you can\Nout of our new guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.54,0:22:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.14,0:22:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.45,0:23:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.51,0:23:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Anytime, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.75,0:23:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Antonio?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.29,0:23:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a long drive\Nback to Princeton.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.65,0:23:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew the place\Nwas empty--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.99,0:23:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a safehouse,\Nnot a crash pad.\NGet out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.79,0:23:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?\NQue paso?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.96,0:23:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The FBI raided\Nthe downtown warehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.20,0:23:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They grabbed Machado.\NThey took back their agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.53,0:23:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Agent? Th-Th-That was an agent\Nyou had captive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.17,0:23:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think\NI wanted you\Nout of there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.50,0:23:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,For your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.91,0:23:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A business matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.11,0:23:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The FBI--\NYeah, it is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.01,0:23:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you need\Nto let us handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.69,0:23:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You should never\Nbe deceived into believing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.39,0:23:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that you can really\Ntrust anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.83,0:23:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My experience is that even\Nmy most intimate partners,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.73,0:23:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,advisers, and friends have\Nhad occasion to betray me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.77,0:24:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You must always be\Nmentally prepared
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.17,0:24:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to separate yourself\Nfrom anyone\Nand anything in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.65,0:24:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Because people will turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.18,0:24:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what\NI'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.05,0:24:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You witnessed it\Nwith Mr. Kaplan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.39,0:24:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell, you've done it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.42,0:24:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry if I made it sound\Nall doom and gloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.33,0:24:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.03,0:24:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.03,0:24:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a freedom\Nin your new role.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.10,0:24:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Freedom from convention.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.74,0:24:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,From being a follower.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.24,0:24:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The pack takes its cue\Nfrom the alpha wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.28,0:24:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And when that wolf\Nis wise and mindful,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.45,0:24:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole pack prospers.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.42,0:24:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That said, you will\Nhave one blind spot,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.36,0:24:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,one weakness that\Ncan't be willed out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.27,0:25:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.57,0:25:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no advice\Nfor you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.61,0:25:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All I can tell you is, uh,\Ndo your best,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.72,0:25:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My company is highly respected\Nin the industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.22,0:25:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you\Nthink happened with\Nyour source code--
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.26,0:25:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You turned my software\Ninto a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.26,0:25:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You took something\Nmeant to help\Nand protect people
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.50,0:25:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and stripped it for parts\Nuntil it was dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.67,0:25:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Agent Mojtabai,\NI've reviewed your file.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.84,0:25:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on what I saw,\Nnothing you've said here\Nsurprises me,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.84,0:25:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,except that you blame us for\Na problem of your own making.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.64,0:25:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you\Ntalking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.48,0:25:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You hired us to do\Nan independent review
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.68,0:25:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,of your source code.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.52,0:25:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Our conclusions\Nwere clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.75,0:25:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you've forgotten\Nhow clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.62,0:25:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You must not have read\Nour report.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.49,0:25:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought you\Nanother copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.83,0:26:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I read it\Ncover-to-cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.23,0:26:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My business partner,\NNick, read it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.17,0:26:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you didn't\Nread it thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.77,0:26:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,See for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.14,0:26:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Aside from\Na few minor glitches,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.34,0:26:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you gave us\Na clean bill of health.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.69,0:26:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What are these sections?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.35,0:26:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Implementations?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.06,0:26:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Vulnerabilities?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.50,0:26:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen\Nany of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.90,0:26:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.07,0:26:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,See, no one needed to turn\Nyour software into a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.24,0:26:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I built a weapon\Nfrom the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.54,0:26:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What time do Conroy and\Nthe others get here tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.55,0:26:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,15, and the buyers should\Narrive shortly after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.99,0:27:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew\Nthis whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.52,0:27:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, you're not supposed\Nto be in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.99,0:27:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Chloe.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.26,0:27:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the godfather\Nof Greylock.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.79,0:27:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who invented us.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.56,0:27:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything we've accomplished\Nis because of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.70,0:27:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to you?\NYou fall off your bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.77,0:27:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember this?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.47,0:27:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a little chat\Nwith Walter Sykes\Nfrom VitasNow,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.74,0:27:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and this is\Ntheir full report,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.74,0:27:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,with all those sections\Nyou didn't bother to show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.78,0:27:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the ones that said\Nthere's vulnerability
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.71,0:27:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Greylock\Nsource code?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.92,0:27:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if you took\Na look around on the way in,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.85,0:27:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but we're way\Npast source code.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.42,0:27:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember Conroy?\NAll that financing?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.32,0:27:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That was\Njust the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.76,0:27:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We're pitching\Nbuyers tomorrow.\NSky's the limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.99,0:27:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You lied to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.06,0:27:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I sat right there\Nand you lied to my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.36,0:27:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I omitted.\NI held a few things back.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.03,0:27:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What did this company know\Nthat you and I didn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.47,0:27:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If something was really wrong,\Nyou would've fixed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.34,0:27:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I was too close\Nto the project.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.97,0:27:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't see it.\NThat is why we hired them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.41,0:27:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how dangerous\Nthis could be?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.44,0:28:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If the wrong person\Nwith the right know-how\Ngot access to Greylock,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.65,0:28:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,they could strip it down\Nto its most dangerous parts
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.78,0:28:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and use it\Nto cripple systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.45,0:28:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Systems have flaws.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.35,0:28:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So do people.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.09,0:28:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And I won't destroy\Nthis company
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.49,0:28:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,because a bad guy\Nmight misuse what we made.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.63,0:28:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They make\Nbaseball bats, Aram.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.23,0:28:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though someone\Nmight use it
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.60,0:28:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to crack somebody\Nover the head--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.80,0:28:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't\Nkeep selling this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.47,0:28:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can as long as clients\Nwant to buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.03,0:28:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There might be a few bad eggs.\NIt happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.10,0:28:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I want this program out there\Nso the rest of our customers
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.01,0:28:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,can use it\Nfor the good you intended.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.34,0:28:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No. You want it out there\Nso you can be rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.48,0:28:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Chloe was right.\NYou shouldn't be in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.18,0:28:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You should leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.02,0:28:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too soon for Marquez
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.78,0:28:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to have gotten\Nout of the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.12,0:28:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's he hiding?\NIn the city? Nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.55,0:28:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know\Nwhere he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.19,0:28:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know\Nwhere he's gonna be.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.99,0:28:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How would you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.16,0:28:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I overheard El Conejo\Nget the second phone call\Nabout his missing shipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.90,0:28:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the time and the place\Nfor the exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.07,0:28:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll share it,\Nfor a trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.44,0:29:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What trade?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.01,0:29:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be sent back\Nto Mexico for trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.28,0:29:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, let me guess--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.85,0:29:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you've got a friend in\Nthe Fiscalia General's office?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.92,0:29:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not gonna be\Nany trial, will there?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.35,0:29:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna worry about\Na little fish like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.92,0:29:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Or go after the big fish\Nlike Marquez?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.36,0:29:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You kidnapped an FBI agent?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.10,0:29:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You threatened him\Nover a truckload of,\Nwhat, vegetables?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.27,0:29:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Avocados are a fruit,\Nimbecile.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.03,0:29:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sick.\NThe both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.07,0:29:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This whole thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.48,0:29:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the day you were born,\NI knew you were weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.95,0:29:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You were built to sit\Nbehind a desk or a library.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.55,0:29:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it, and I let you\Nstay soft-- to keep you safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.59,0:29:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you ever question\Nmy judgment\Nor my control again,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.29,0:29:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,so help me, boy,\Nyou will learn a lesson
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.26,0:29:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,in what a real man of power\Ncan do.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.34,0:30:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you wait here,\Nuntil we're long gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.29,0:30:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There will come a time,\NElizabeth,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.53,0:30:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,when you are\Ncompletely stumped,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.56,0:30:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,a time when you will have\Nfactored in every variable
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.57,0:30:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and you still\Nwon't see the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.60,0:30:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But it'll be there.\NSomewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.80,0:30:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer is--\Nis always there.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.81,0:30:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you can't see it,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.68,0:30:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it's because some assumption\Nthat you've made,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.61,0:30:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,something you've taken\Nfor granted is false.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.32,0:30:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you're in a hospital\Nin France.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.48,0:30:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It may not be France\Nor a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.49,0:30:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be New York\Nand a warehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.82,0:31:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The magician\Ndoesn't trick you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.36,0:31:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The magician helps you\Ntrick yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.34,0:31:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That looks fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.81,0:31:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheecha's a god-send.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.77,0:31:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pain free and looser\Nthan a kangaroo's tummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.98,0:31:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's a trick,\Nan illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.15,0:31:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.99,0:31:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh. Yeah. Oh, baby! Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.10,0:31:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to know\Nwho got into my safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.63,0:31:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've been asking\Nwhether this is my safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.84,0:31:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They tore mine out.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.18,0:31:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see\Nexactly where there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.61,0:31:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And they replaced it\Nwith a perfect replica.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.11,0:31:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they were free to take\Nthe original safe somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.85,0:31:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and drill for days\Nif they needed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.05,0:32:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How did Kosta not know?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.35,0:32:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.86,0:32:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,An afternoon away.\NAn evening at the opera.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.56,0:32:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.50,0:32:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That was then.\NThe now is in Zurich.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.66,0:32:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And his name is\NHeinrich Zimmerstahl.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.94,0:32:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought your ransom.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.17,0:32:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But we both know you're never\Ngonna touch a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.94,0:32:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Because\Nyou're not leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.35,0:33:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is now\Nyour graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.65,0:33:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I bury you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.32,0:33:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?\NWe don't have\Nthe shipment yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.12,0:33:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.09,0:33:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,His only way out of here\Nis through us,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.42,0:33:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and he won't even\Nget that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.93,0:33:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I want\Nto get caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.56,0:33:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Antonio?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.50,0:33:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What in God's name\Nare you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.77,0:33:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I still seem weak to you?\NLike I belong behind a desk?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.07,0:33:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta be joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.64,0:33:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How many years of it\Ndo you think I could stand it,\NDad?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.47,0:33:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.88,0:33:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Of not being allowed to know\Nabout the family business.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.34,0:33:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Of not getting a phone call\Nwhen my own father\Nis just a few hours away.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.58,0:33:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not strong enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.48,0:33:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean\Nnot Samuel enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.72,0:33:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It has nothing\Nto do with Samuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.39,0:33:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I always wanted\Nthe best for you. Always!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.76,0:33:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted me gone.\NThe college boy in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.33,0:33:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I outsmarted you.\NI took your truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.86,0:33:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I ransomed it back\Nright under your nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.70,0:33:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.43,0:33:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I strong enough now?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.17,0:34:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Get down!\NFBI!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.14,0:34:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Get down!\NYou think you're\Nso smart, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.28,0:34:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!\NDown!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.61,0:34:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You led the FBI\Nright to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.68,0:34:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? How about you\Nand your ego?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.01,0:34:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kidnapping.\NCalling attention to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.68,0:34:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.02,0:34:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It was you?\NThis whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.32,0:34:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I did\Nwhat I had to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.46,0:34:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.\NHe's paying attention now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.13,0:34:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You want my attention?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.29,0:34:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to be part\Nof this business?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.73,0:34:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Okay, how about\Nwe de-escalate?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.23,0:34:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a cost\Nto this business!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.40,0:34:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can talk about it\Nin family therapy tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.53,0:34:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is what happens\Nwhen you cross El Conejo.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.30,0:34:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.84,0:34:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- Drop it!\N- I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.21,0:34:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.81,0:34:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're okay.\NHe needs an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.51,0:34:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you?\NI'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.81,0:34:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm never touching\Nan avocado again.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.69,0:34:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost died today\Nbecause of you, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.56,0:34:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.93,0:34:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think\Nit would go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.43,0:35:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think\Nhe would...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.71,0:35:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you even\Ninvolved in this?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.07,0:35:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my code you used\Nto hack your dad's business.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.58,0:35:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?\NTh-That's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.55,0:35:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.52,0:35:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you even get ahold\Nof it to begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.08,0:35:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, my roommate\Nat Princeton.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.59,0:35:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a\Ncomputer science major.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.86,0:35:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He saw a beta test version\Nof the--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.59,0:35:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Of your software\Nin his programming class.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.80,0:35:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He made some minor tweaks,\Ntook the rootkit,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.73,0:35:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,made it offensive,\Nsaw how dangerous\Nand adaptable it was,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.47,0:35:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and said he needed\Nto test it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.84,0:35:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the perfect target--\Nmy father.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.67,0:35:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Your roommate weaponized\Nmy code in a dorm room?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.08,0:35:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He said it was\Nthe perfect weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.51,0:35:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know.\NYou built it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.33,0:36:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Kosta.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.13,0:36:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I would never betray you,\NRaymond, but I did fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.83,0:36:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You left this house safe\Nwith me,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.87,0:36:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and somehow,\NI let the enemy slip inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.27,0:36:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I walked by that safe\Nhundreds of times,\Nand I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.14,0:36:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't have.\NI didn't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.94,0:36:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just\Na good guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.71,0:36:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,When this is over,\Nthe house and everything in it\Nare yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.69,0:36:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it, sell it.\NI don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.19,0:36:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.53,0:36:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll forgive me if I let you\Nsee yourself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.57,0:36:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Zimmerstahl\Nhas arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.31,0:36:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.55,0:36:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been years.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.95,0:36:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I was telling\Nyour associate here
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.49,0:37:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,about the first time\Nwe met.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.49,0:37:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The St. Moritz\NSnow Polo World Cup, 2005.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.99,0:37:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't gone near a drop\Nof peppermint schnapps since.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.66,0:37:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.86,0:37:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,When I came to see you\Nall those years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.37,0:37:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you I needed\Na particularly secure safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.94,0:37:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you that safe needed\Nto be one-of-a-kind.\NDo you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.34,0:37:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.35,0:37:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really going through\Nwith it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.99,0:37:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I can think of a thousand\Nterrible things
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.82,0:37:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the wrong person could do\Nif the Greylock code\Nwent wide,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.53,0:37:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but what scares me most are\Nthe things I cannot think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.53,0:37:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to stop this\Nbefore Nick\Ngets more funding.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.67,0:37:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing\Nthe right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.38,0:38:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch your step.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.18,0:38:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.35,0:38:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened? Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.95,0:38:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That box was one of the finest\NI'd ever constructed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.02,0:38:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't agree more.\NOne of the finest.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.49,0:38:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem--\Nthat's not my safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.40,0:38:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My safe is gone, and the one\Nin its place is identical.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.67,0:38:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,One person is capable\Nof that kind of craftsmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.11,0:38:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.58,0:38:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You built a second safe,\Ndidn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.28,0:38:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.25,0:38:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.39,0:38:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a second.\NIdentical.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.59,0:38:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,For whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.19,0:38:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Raymond, I made it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.28,0:39:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Having problems\Nwith your source code, Nick?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.91,0:39:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this you?\NDid you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.11,0:39:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing in Greylock\Nwill respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.85,0:39:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And you didn't even start\Nthe space camp program\Nfor those kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.25,0:39:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.42,0:39:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over, Nick.\NI went into the servers.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.82,0:39:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I undid the architecture,\Nframework, databases--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.26,0:39:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Aram, I have a buyers'\Npresentation in 10 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.99,0:39:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Conroy's in there.\NThree other angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.23,0:39:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I\Nsupposed to tell them?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.30,0:39:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell them the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.00,0:39:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.20,0:39:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not too late.\NYou can fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.67,0:39:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I could, but I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.54,0:39:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And it would take the best\NIT team in the world months
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.01,0:39:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,to undo what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.85,0:39:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.28,0:39:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.72,0:39:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,what's already been done\Nwith our software?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.49,0:39:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A couple of idiot kids\Nin a dorm room
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.79,0:39:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,used it to hack\Na drug cartel.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.96,0:39:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the next person\Nwho gets their hands on it
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.76,0:39:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and knows how to modify\Nthe rootkit?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.26,0:39:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what the hell\Nyou're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.86,0:39:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't think\Nyou ever did.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.87,0:40:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My code was never safe\Nwith you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.90,0:40:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what you tell them\Nin the other room?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.97,0:40:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You tell them that\Nyour ex-business partner
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.84,0:40:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,did what he set out\Nto do.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.24,0:40:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He tried to make the world\Na little safer.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.05,0:40:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you come in a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.70,0:40:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Reggie Cole is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.70,0:40:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The trail on the gunman\Nwent cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.03,0:40:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but there is one lead\Nleft to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.94,0:40:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The lawyer.\NWhat was his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.67,0:40:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Lacroix.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.21,0:40:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The man must've\Nhad associates,\Na legal practice, a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.04,0:40:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's find out everything\Nwe can about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.91,0:40:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.\NWhat do we have to lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.85,0:40:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I have everything to lose,\Nbut that's not gonna stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.02,0:40:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.19,0:40:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea you were\Ngoing to be robbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.99,0:41:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You say you made\Nthe duplicate for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.83,0:41:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no.\NNot you directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.56,0:41:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Then who?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.73,0:41:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.30,0:41:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She came to me and she said\Nshe was your representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.94,0:41:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She knew\Neverything about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.77,0:41:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She knew everything\Nabout the safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.94,0:41:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She was clear\Nshe wanted it made
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.14,0:41:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,to the same specifications\Nas the original.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.35,0:41:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She paid with\Nthe same bank accounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.38,0:41:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing different\Nwas using uncoded
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.39,0:41:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,ready-to-set biometric panels\Nfor the thumb scan.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.69,0:41:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyone could open\Nthe new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.63,0:41:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time, I assumed\Nyou'd simply set it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.43,0:41:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me everything that you\Ncan remember about the woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.77,0:41:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oof. It was so long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.34,0:41:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.38,0:41:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She wasn't very tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.22,0:41:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I do remember\None other thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.95,0:42:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.05,0:42:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened several times.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.26,0:42:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She called me "deary."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.99,0:42:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Deary?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.16,0:42:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And she called herself\N"Mister."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.30,0:42:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaplan?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.77,0:42:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.03,0:42:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kaplan.
